properties.areaDesc: Juneau Borough and Northern Admiralty Island
properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued February 1 at 5:22AM AKST until February 2 at 3:00AM AKST by NWS Juneau AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow. Accumulations of 3 to 8 inches.

* WHERE...Juneau Borough and Northern Admiralty Island.

* WHEN...Until 3 AM AKST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Travel could be very difficult. Visibility will be
very poor in heavier snow showers.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Amounts will be highly variable with
heaviest showers most likely this afternoon and this evening.
There will be periods of little or no snowfall followed by
moderate to heavy snow squalls.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

For the latest road conditions call 5 1 1 or visit
511.alaska.gov.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 3 AM AKST SUNDAY FOR JUNEAU
